Africa

As of **February 2026**, the legal and activist landscape surrounding resource exploitation in Africa has reached a critical boiling point. The traditional "corporate impunity" model is being systematically dismantled in European courts.

Below are the most current details, legal resources, and direct calls to action for your web app.

